N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 81.4 - Registration of device

State Regulations

If no objection is received within the 20-day period, the
commissioner shall register the device, and upon request shall issue a
certificate of registration to the labor organization. Notes
